summary: It’s Apple Event day, which means it’ll soon be time to score drafts, picks, and (for the first time here) Bingo cards.  I’ve put together 24 things that I think could happen during today’s keynote video.  You’ll notice, though, that some items are contradictory — I think they could go either way...
title: ‘It’s Glowtime’ Apple Event Bingo, HeyDingus Edition
